      "text": "（どうして？　体が思うように動いてくれない……）\n（みんなが私をフォローするように動いてる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4803834279,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura Kawasaki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "（調子の悪い私に合わせてくれてる……）\n（私、みんなの足を引っ張ってる……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.0666690827,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
