      "text": "実は、過労で倒れてからずっと調子が悪いんです\nまだ疲れが取れていないのかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.5000003816,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-01-noon",
      "startTime": 166.7462458295
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "医者",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_02-doctor002.m4a",
      "text": "疲れのせいもあると思うが\nもしかすると、他にも原因があるかもしれないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 169.079593913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "医者",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_02/sud_vo_adv_main_04_10_02-doctor003.m4a",
      "text": "いつも元気だから忘れそうになるが\n川咲さんの体は普通の人とは違う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.179593913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
